title: Peri Peri Chicken Tray Bake with Wedges and Peri Mayo
description: Peri Peri. The Portuguese marinade so delicious, they named it twice. We’ve given this traditionally fiery sauce a milder, family-friendly flavour and combined it with honey, red wine vinegar, oregano and oil for a taste that won’t disappoint. With minimal prep time and washing uo, this is a great min-week winner. Clean plates all round.
